
- const r = React.createElement;

// react: SelectGuide

- const platformIcon = {position: 'absolute', top: '10px', left: '31px'};
- const platformTitle = {fontSize: '16px', margin: '16px 0px 0px 101px'};
- const platformDesc = {fontSize: '12px', margin: '0px 0px 18px 101px'};

div(style={fontFamily: "'Lato', sans-serif", padding: '24px'})

  h4(style={color:'#4a4a4a', fontSize: '13px', margin: '0px'}) GET STARTED NOW!

  p(style={fontSize: '31px', margin: '17px 0px 13px'})
    | Which platform are you getting to start with?

  p(style={fontSize: '16px', margin: '0px 0px 19px'})
    | Choose your platform for developing your app with Skygear.

  div(style= new PlatformStyle('ios'), onClick=setSDK('ios'))
